* Objects of this type are returned from the {@link Ctx#onAttach(Runnable)}, * {@link Ctx#onCancel(Runnable)} and {@link Ctx#onDetach(Runnable)} methods of {@link Ctx}. *

* The {@link #dispose()} method will remove that callback from the Ctx.
* Disposes a callback. Behavior is undefined if invoked more than once.
